const name = prompt("What's your name?");
Type your name and click OK

alert(`Hello ${name}`);
Displays Hello yourname


Prompt a user to enter their first and last name and display the following.
O/P
Enter your First Name: Pam
Enter your Last Name: Chan
Hello, Pam Chan

Solution:
let fName = prompt("Enter your First Name:");
let lName = prompt("Enter your Last Name:");
alert(`Hello, ${fName} ${lName}`);